<h3>Terms that should be avoided</h3>
The following terms should be <strong>avoided in our community</strong> as they are either highly insulting or are non-inclusive. Recommendations for what to use instead are included.<br />
&nbsp;
<table border="0" cellpadding="0" cellspacing="0" style="width: 100%;">
	<thead>
		<tr>
